n\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 09, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104glg1665702714695.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/glg1665702714695.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/glg1665702714695.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"glg1665702714695\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Menu Bar\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Name of the menu bar initially displayed for the current form or application shell.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"glg1665702714695__section_w5116ab1b5b1_w5117ab1b5_w5118ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"glg1665702714695__table_d11750e1_d11751e1_d11752e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">Expected Value:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">String of up to 32 characters. Supports Unicode.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">Default Value:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">None</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"glg1665702714695__section_yk2_x5l_twb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d854201e97\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"glg1665702714695__p_d100445e1_d100446e1_d100447e1\">Forms that do not have their own menu bar use the\n            application menu bar.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"glg1665702714695__p_d100448e1_d100449e1_d100450e1\">The values of the assignment settings\n               <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$LANGUAGE</span> and <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$VARIATION</span> affect which menu bars\n            are used at run time.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"glg1665702714695__section_kfr_y5l_twb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d854201e115\">Applies To</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"glg1665702714695__ul_jlt_z5l_twb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"glg1665702714695__li_d40511e1_d40512e1_d40513e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"yye1705472567076.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yye1705472567076.html\" title=\"An application shell is the first object that is executed when a Windows or character mode application is started. It determines how the application is initialized and the first form component that is displayed.\">Application Shells for Desktop Applications</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"glg1665702714695__li_d40514e1_d40515e1_d40516e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"usl1704692305727.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/usl1704692305727.html\" title=\"Form components provide the user interface for Uniface desktop applications. They are always executed on the client system and can be modal (form retains focus until it is closed) or non-modal (users can switch focus to other forms).\">Forms</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vfw1705577424699.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Menu Objects</a><p>Uniface enables you to define menu bar, drop-down menu, and pop-up menu objects for use in Windows applications.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zum1665703230237.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$LANGUAGE</a><p>Specify the language to use for global objects and language setups.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fcq1665703251101.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$VARIATION</a><p>Specify the library name for global objects needed by the application when the application starts. Libraries are typed, so each global object library can have the same name which functions as a shared namespace which can be specified by this setting.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3613283\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3613283\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Menu Bar Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 09, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Menu Bar Name of the menu bar initially displayed for the current form or application shell. Expected Value: String of up to 32 characters. Supports Unicode. Default Value: None Description Forms that do not have their own menu bar use the application menu bar. The values of the assignment settings $LANGUAGE and $VARIATION affect which menu bars are used at run time. Applies To Application Shells for Desktop Applications Forms Related Links Menu Objects Uniface enables you to define menu bar, drop-down menu, and pop-up menu objects for use in Windows applications. $LANGUAGE Specify the language to use for global objects and language setups. $VARIATION Specify the library name for global objects needed by the application when the application starts. Libraries are typed, so each global object library can have the same name which functions as a shared namespace which can be specified by this setting. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}